The intruders appropriated 11 of the 13 apartments in the building in Balmes, 51
12 of the occupiers left the house yesterday at noon without resisting
All indications are that the nightmare experienced by neighbors from number 51 in Balmes Street is finally over.
Twelve people voluntarily left the building they illegally occupied and where they organized gigantic parties that woke neighbors at noon. They left the building by order of the court and without having to intervene the police.
